{
  "stem": "19690.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 63.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "As far as [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] things that happened, we-- I think the happiest times were on weekends, when my other uncle, my uncle Ernst, would drive to Mannheim or Heidelberg for an afternoon and evening-- maybe a play for the children, maybe just going up to the castle in Heidelberg, to see something a little bit different.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And even then, I remember in Heidelberg, one of the favorite kaffee houses, where we would go in the afternoon for some cake, all of a sudden had a sign on the door, Jews not wanted.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And of course, you didn't try to go past that, even if you thought you might be able to pass.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It wasn't worth it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the same signs started appearing in Speyer at certain stores also.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So you-- it became more and more restrictive as to what you could and what you couldn't do.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] population also became more, I would say, antagonistic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They would either ignore you completely or they would just say, Jew, don't come here anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Or, if they were-- we were old customers, they would even-- and some of them did that at great risk-- say, don't come here anymore.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We'll deliver to you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And then in the night, the doorbell would ring.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they would deliver, so nobody could see, things like hard goods.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "As far as [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] foods, we were able to get.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "The grocer and the baker-- there were two bakeries within walking distance.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And there was a grocery store at the corner.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And we could go there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And we had no problem getting foodstuffs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But other things, we would have to go to Mannheim sometimes or to Heidelberg in order to pick up clothes and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
